<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3154758" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="2"><ahelp hid=".uno:Calculate">Recalculates the current sheet. Use <item type="menuitem">Tools - Cell Contents - Recalculate</item> or press <item type="keycode">F9</item> to recalculate all changed formulas in the current sheet. Press <item type="keycode">Shift+Ctrl+F9</item> to recalculate all cells in all sheets.</ahelp></paragraph>
